results.name: Value of n-th cyclotomic polynomial at n.
link: G. C. Greubel, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..250
Eric Weisstein's World of Mathematics, Cyclotomic Polynomial
example: n=10: 10th cyclotomic polynomial is 1-x+x^2-x^3+x^4; at x=10 it gives a(10)=9091.
